  "text": "The transmission-line measurement setup consists of a stripline structure where the CNTs replace the metallic trace of the stripline structure shown in Fig . 2 . The reflection (S II ) and transmission (S 2 1 ) coefficients are then measured to extract the complex effective permittivity of the metallic trace composed ofCNT networks as described in [CITATION_1] .",
